#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module allows you to set up the actions you want to associate when you "
"plug new devices."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul vam omogoča, da nastavite dejanja, ki jih želite povezati, ko "
"priključite nove naprave."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the Device Actions Manager</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona upravitelja dejanj naprave</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the Device Actions Manager</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona upravitelja dejanj naprave</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will see listed all of the possible actions that are available when "
"devices are plugged in. Please note that they will only be available under "
"certain conditions."
msgstr ""
"Prikazani bodo vsa možna dejanja, ki so na voljo, ko so naprave priključene. "
"Upoštevajte, da bodo na voljo le pod določenimi pogoji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> This will ask you to supply a name for your new "
"action, then will open that action for editing. If you do not supply all the "
"required details in that dialog, then your action will be deleted."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> To vas bo pozvalo k vnosu imena za novo "
"dejanje, nato pa bo odprlo to dejanje za urejanje. Če v tem pogovornem oknu "
"ne navedete vseh zahtevanih podatkov, bo vaše dejanje izbrisano."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Edit</guibutton> This will allow you to change the Name, Icon, "
"command to execute and the conditions the action must match to be shown."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> S tem lahko spremenite Ime, Ikono, ukaz za "
"izvedbo in pogoje, ki jih mora dejanje izpolnjevati, da se prikaže."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Discard / Cannot be deleted / Remove</guibutton> This will do "
"different actions, depending on if it was supplied with your system or "
"created by you. You can only discard changes to system wide actions, if "
"there are no changes then these actions cannot be deleted. User created "
"actions are completely removed, including all changes."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Odstrani / Ni mogoče izbrisati / Odstrani</guibutton> Ta gumb bo "
"opravil različna dejanja, odvisno od tega, ali je bil dobavljen s sistemom "
"ali ste ga ustvarili sami. Zavrnete lahko samo spremembe v sistemskih "
"dejanjih, če ni sprememb, teh dejanj ni mogoče izbrisati. Dejanja, ki jih je "
"ustvaril uporabnik, so v celoti odstranjena, vključno z vsemi spremembami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Action"
msgstr "Dodaj dejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button brings you a dialog to enter the new "
"action name."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> prikaže pogovorno okno za vnos imena "
"novega dejanja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the Add Action dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Dodaj dejanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the Add Action dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Dodaj dejanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The action name should correctly describe the action. After entering a name "
"and clicking <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, the Edit Action dialog will show to "
"allow you to set up the action properties."
msgstr ""
"Ime dejanja mora pravilno opisovati dejanje. Ko vnesete ime in kliknete "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>, se prikaže pogovorno okno Uredi dejanje, v "
"katerem lahko nastavite lastnosti akcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Action"
msgstr "Uredi dejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows you to change the settings of the action you selected."
msgstr "V tem pogovornem oknu lahko spremenite nastavitve izbranega dejanja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the Edit Action dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Uredi dejanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the Edit Action dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Uredi dejanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This includes the icon, the action name, the action command and the various "
"parameters. You can change the icon by clicking on it."
msgstr ""
"To vključuje ikono, ime akcije, ukaz akcije in različne parametre. Ikono "
"lahko spremenite tako, da jo kliknete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The parameters are displayed in a tree, the top item having to be true in "
"order for the action to be shown."
msgstr ""
"Parametri so prikazani v drevesu, pri čemer mora biti zgornji element "
"resničen, da se dejanje prikaže."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit parameter"
msgstr "Uredi parameter"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter type"
msgstr "Tip parametra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This controls what can be contained inside it, or what matching is performed "
"to check if it is true."
msgstr ""
"S tem se nadzoruje, kaj je lahko vsebovano v njem ali kakšno ujemanje se "
"izvede, da se preveri, ali je resničen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Property Match"
msgstr "Lastniško ujemanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compares the specified property of the Device (using <guilabel>Device type</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Value name</guilabel>) and using the evaluator, "
"compares it against the text provided."
msgstr ""
"Primerja določeno lastnost Naprave (z uporabo <guilabel>Tip naprave</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Naziv vrednosti</guilabel>) in jo s pomočjo "
"ocenjevalnika primerja z navedenim besedilom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Content Conjunction"
msgstr "Povezava vsebine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "All sub-properties of this must be true for it to be true itself."
msgstr "Vse podlastnosti tega morajo biti resnične, da je resnično tudi samo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Content Disjunction"
msgstr "Vsebinska disjunkcija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any sub-property of this may be true for it to be true itself."
msgstr ""
"Katera koli podlastnost tega je lahko resnična, da bi bila resnična tudi "
"sama po sebi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device interface match"
msgstr "Ujemanje vmesnika naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checks to see if the Device can be classed as the selected Device type."
msgstr "Preveri, ali je napravo mogoče uvrstiti v izbran tip naprave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device type"
msgstr "Tip naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are the possible device types supported by &plasma; on your system. "
"They are used in both Property and Device interface matches."
msgstr ""
"To so vse možne vrste naprav, ki jih podpira &plasma; na vašem sistemu. "
"Uporabljajo se pri ujemanju vmesnikov lastnosti in naprav."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Value name"
msgstr "Ime vrednosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a list of all possible property names for the selected device type. "
"It also provides the selection of the value evaluator (which is either "
"<guilabel>Equals</guilabel> or <guilabel>Contains</guilabel>), and allows "
"entry of the text to be compared with."
msgstr ""
"To je seznam vseh možnih imen lastnosti za izbrano vrsto naprave. Omogoča "
"tudi izbiro ocenjevalnika vrednosti (ki je <guilabel >Enako</guilabel > ali "
"<guilabel >Vsebuje</guilabel >) in omogoča vnos besedila, s katerim se "
"primerja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset Parameter"
msgstr "Ponastavi parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reverts any unsaved changes you have made to this parameter."
msgstr ""
"Razveljavi vse neshranjene spremembe, ki ste jih naredili v tem parametru."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Parameter changes"
msgstr "Shrani spremembe parametrov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the changes you have made to the parameter."
msgstr "Shrani spremembe, ki ste jih naredili v parametru."

